#

  ## Digital Signature Verification

The file `artifact.txt` was signed using the RSA private key.

The generated artifacts are:

- `artifact.txt`
- `artifact.sig`
- `public_key.pem`

These are stored in:

`labs/02-week-02-cryptography-fundamentals/submissions/signatures/`

### Successful Verification

The screenshot below shows that the signature verification succeeded before the file was modified.

![Verified OK](../../assets/screenshots/week-02/digital-signature-verified-ok.png)

### Verification Failure After Tampering

After adding the word `tampered` to `artifact.txt`, verification fails because the file content changed.

![Verification failure](../../assets/screenshots/week-02/digital-signature-verification-failure.png)
